flowRoot.flowPara: This card is just to show, that there are consumer devices that can communicate with satellites without a big dish. Eg. Spot3 can transmit only a few bytes, but that would be sufficient to get eg. new keys for a bigger global surveillance nightmare or to activate a CodeRED against a person that asks to much relevant question, identified maybe by something like a GUID (Global Unique IDentifier)
